query:
SELECT album.*, COUNT(media_album.media) AS count
                FROM user_catalog
                    JOIN album USING (catalog)
                    JOIN album_descendent USING (id)
                    LEFT JOIN media_album ON album_descendent.descendent=media_album.album
                WHERE
                    user_catalog.user=$1 AND
                    album.id=$2
                GROUP BY album.id
